cs.HC, cs.UM, cs.MM, cs.IR, cs.SI 

The paper discusses challenges in integrating personal and intimate mobile and wearable devices into multi-device ecosystems. This topic falls under the Human-Computer Interaction (cs.HC) sub-category. Additionally, the paper discusses user modeling (cs.UM) and information retrieval (cs.IR) in the context of multi-device ecosystems. The paper also discusses multimedia (cs.MM) and social and information networks (cs.SI) in the context of multi-device ecosystems.
